			<div class="post-6819 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-constitution category-politics tag-10th-amendment tag-american-history tag-federal-government tag-federal-register tag-force-bill tag-jury-nullification-in-the-united-states tag-law-schools tag-nullification tag-patrick-henry tag-politics-of-the-united-states tag-speeches tag-thomas-jefferson tag-thomas-woods tag-tom-wood tag-tom-woods tag-united-states tag-virginia post_box top" id="post-6819">
